POPULATION: ONE also features a wide variety of rotating PvP and PvE modes for your squad to play including:\n\n\u25cf Battle Royale\n\n\u25cf Phoenix Royale\n\n\u25cf Sandbox: Player-created Games (Custom maps and rules) \n\n\u25cf Team Deathmatch with customizable loadouts\n\n\u25cf War mode (12v12)\n\n\u25cf Legions mode (6v6v6v6)\n\n\u25cf Metropolis Royale\n\n\u25cf Single Player Mode\n\n\u25cf Co-Op Bot Battle\n\n\u25cf Duos\n\n\u25cf Hangouts \n\n\u25cf Training Park Practice and Social Hub\n\n\n*Limited time offer. Offer subject to restrictions and change without notice.\n", "short_description": "THE NUMBER #1 VR BATTLE ROYALE IS FREE TO PLAY!\n\nGET POPULATION:ONE TODAY AND GET 300 IN-GAME GOLD*\n\nCLIMB, FLY, BUILD. POPULATION: ONE  is a multiplayer, First Person Shooter, Battle Royale, only possible in VR. Even better, now with POP1 Sandbox, an in-game user generated game creator, you can build custom games - your map, your rules!"}]}, "developer_name": "BigBox VR, Inc.", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://www.bigboxvr.com/privacy-policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.bigboxvr.com/terms-and-conditions.html", "publisher_name": "BigBox VR, Inc.", "support_website_url": "http://www.bigboxvr.com/contact.html", "website_url": "http://www.PopulationOneVR.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "3744040075834813"}, {"id": "1990104051447093"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "ARCADE", "SHOOTER"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "fr", "es_MX", "ja", "ko", "de"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "ST