t=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDqAOGtqW_c1N7car3VzSbfOjuTOz4o3R7hZ4sAIt9Czg&oe=67308646"}, {"file_name": "ss2Climbing01.png", "id": "367429307608287", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75280981_367429310941620_8894710312874754090_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KlLM97IbubMQ7kNvgFuJ3KX&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAsh6OMJeEzQ29QnCKX3m5cE_n8janWKOHrsRjN9m1omQ&oe=6730AABE"}, {"file_name": "ss3Vista01.png", "id": "774945693324752", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86609237_774945696658085_6695766518862910198_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3Zpv9jSHMSsQ7kNvgEzuR7I&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAa_gnG9kJMwWdMc87P1tPfm6EMVDGc6woqO9ameN7JcQ&oe=6730947C"}, {"file_name": "ss4Fistbump01.png", "id": "978037232672345", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75404381_978037239339011_4394586620234105676_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=JlKFJ6P8IJUQ7kNvgG44Wcj&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBX5lR1BjEWmVmcv4eoUZ3GXZ4o7L4xC11x-mqg1tUHRQ&oe=6730A063"}, {"file_name": "ss5Fying01.png", "id": "321577395576633", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974466_321577398909966_3454827555435888588_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=8SorPV3op8EQ7kNvgErT7hU&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCQ9zxoh9IaXFa2sbFmAmrArLRkzCRes-MQ56dbKzGfcw&oe=67309EE9"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "POPULATION: ONE", "keywords": ["Shooter", "Climbing", "Stream", "Multiplayer", "Games"], "long_description": "CLIMB, FLY, BUILD. Battle Royale only possible in VR.\n \nDrop into a colorful, near future world with limitless combat possibilities. Welcome to POPULATION: ONE, where you and your squad must fight together to survive until the end. \n \nPOPULATION: ONE delivers unparalleled vertical freedom and mobility with its unique Vertical combat System. Fly through the map to rain down bullets from above. Climb anything you see to gain the high ground advantage. Build strategic cover to protect your squad. Use your environment to FIGHT ANYWHERE. \n \nIn POPULATION: ONE, the action never stops with ongoing live in-game events and fresh content to explore.", "short_description": "CLIMB, FLY, BUILD. Battle Royale only possible in VR.\n \nDrop into a colorful, near future world with limitless combat possibilities. \n \nPOPULATION: ONE delivers unparalleled vertical freedom and mobility with its unique Vertical combat System. Fly through the map to rain down bullets from above. Climb anything you see to gain the high ground advantage. Build strategic cover to protect your squad. Use your environment to FIGHT ANYWHERE."}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "385464039520727", "locale": "fr_FR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "POPULATION: ONE", "keywords": ["Shooter", "Climbing"], "long_description": "GRIMPEZ, VOLEZ, CONSTRUISEZ. La Battle Royale qui n'est possible qu'en r\u00e9alit\u00e9 virtuelle.\n\nPlongez au c\u0153ur d'un monde futuriste aux couleurs chatoyantes, o\u00f9 le combat et la guerre ne connaissent aucune limite. Bienvenue dans POPULATION: ONE, un jeu dans lequel vous et votre escouade devez conjuguer vos efforts pour survivre jusqu'\u00e0 la fin.\n\nAvec son syst\u00e8me de combat vertical hors norme, POPULATION: ONE conf\u00e8re une libert\u00e9 d'action et de mouvement exceptionnelle. Survolez la carte pour pilonner vos ennemis. Ascensionnez n'importe quel obstacle pour profiter des avantages tactiques qu'offre un terrain sur\u00e9lev\u00e9. Construisez des abris strat\u00e9giques pour prot\u00e9ger votre escouade. Utilisez votre environnement pour COMBATTRE N'IMPORTE O\u00d9 ! \n\nDans POPULATION: ONE, l'action est non-stop gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 des \u00e9v\u00e9nements constamment organis\u00e9s au sein du jeu et du contenu in\u00e9dit \u00e0 explorer.", "short_description": "GRIMPEZ, VOLEZ, CONSTRUISEZ. La Battle Royale qui n'est possible qu'en r\u00e9alit\u00e9 virtuelle.\n\nPlongez au c\u0153ur d'un monde futuriste aux couleurs chatoyantes, o\u00f9 le combat et la guerre ne connaissent aucune limite. Bienvenue dans POPULATION: ONE, un jeu dans lequel vous et votre escouade devez conjuguer vos efforts pour survivre jusqu'\u00e0 la fin."}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "329048231683525", "locale": "ko_KR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "\ud30c\ud4f0\ub808\uc774\uc158: \uc6d0", "keywords": ["Shooter", "Climbing"], "long_description": "\uc624\ub974\uace0, \ube44\ud589\ud558\uace0, \uac74\uc124\ud558\ub77c. VR\uc5d0\uc11c\ub9cc \uac00\ub2a5\ud55c Battle Royale.\n\n\uc804\ud22c\uac00 \ub04a\uc774\uc9c0 \uc54a\ub294 \ud654\ub824\ud55c \uadfc\ubbf8\ub798 \uc138\uacc4\uc5d0 \ub6f0\uc5b4\ub4dc\uc2ed\uc2dc\uc624. \ud30c\ud4f0\ub808\uc774\uc158: \uc6d0\uc5d0 \uc624\uc2e0 \uac83\uc744 \ud658\uc601\ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4. \ud300\uc6d0\ub4e4\uacfc \ud568\uaed8 \uc2f8\uc6cc \ub05d\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc0b4\uc544\ub0a8\uc73c\uc2ed\uc2dc\uc624. \n\n\ud30c\ud4f0\ub808\uc774\uc158: \uc6d0\uc740 \ud2b9\uc720\uc758 \ubc84\ud2f0\uceec \uc804\ud22c \uc2dc\uc2a4\ud15c\uc73c\ub85c \uc804\ub840 \uc5c6\uc774 \uc790\uc720\ub85c\uc6b4 \ubc84\ud2f0\uceec \ud50c\ub808\uc774\ub97c \uc120\uc0ac\ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4. \ub9f5 \uc704\ub97c \ub0a0\uba70 \ucd1d\uc54c\uc744 \ube44\ucc98\ub7fc \ud37c\ubd80\uc73c\uc2ed\uc2dc\uc624. \ub208\uc5d0 \ubcf4\uc774\ub294 \ubaa8\ub4e0 \uac83\ub4e4\uc5d0 \uae30\uc5b4\uc62c\ub77c \uace0\uc9c0\ub97c \uc120\uc810\ud558\uc2ed\uc2dc\uc624. \uc804\ub7b5\uc801 \uc5c4\ud3d0\ubb3c\uc744 \uac74\uc124\ud574 \ud300\uc744 \ubcf4\ud638\ud558\uc2ed\uc2dc\uc624. \uc5b4\ub514\uc11c\ub3c4 \uc2f8\uc6b8 \uc218 \uc788\uac8c \uc8fc\uc704 \ud658\uacbd\uc744 \uc774\uc6a9\ud558\uc2ed\uc2dc\uc624. \n\n\ud30c\ud4f0\ub808\uc774\uc158: \uc6d0\uc758 \uc561\uc1